# GarminSights Frontend Environment Variables
#
# For local development: leave VITE_API_URL unset (or empty) and the
# Vite dev server will proxy /api/* requests to http://localhost:8000.
#
# For web/cloud deployment: set VITE_API_URL to your deployed backend URL.
# The value is baked into the static build at build time.
#
# Example (production):
# VITE_API_URL=https://api.yourdomain.com

# VITE_API_URL=
